column4: Martin McAleese resigns from the Seanad.[14]
Hildegarde Naughton appointed, replacing Martin McAleese.[15]
Deirdre Clune resigns from the Seanad after being elected to the European Parliament.[9]
Gerard Craughwell wins by-election to replace Deirdre Clune.[10]
Jimmy Harte resigns from the Seanad.[11]
